# 🚀 **LearnAgent: AI-Powered Learning Platform**  

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10+-blue)  
![Streamlit](https://img.shields.io/badge/streamlit-supported-brightgreen)  
![FastAPI](https://img.shields.io/badge/FastAPI-powered-green)  
![OpenAI](https://img.shields.io/badge/OpenAI-GPT-orange)  

**LearnAgent** is an AI-powered platform designed to create **personalized learning experiences**. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced learner, LearnAgent dynamically generates **structured lessons** tailored to your **topic, difficulty level, and learning preference**.  

🎯 **Built With:**  
✅ **FastAPI** - Backend API for lesson generation  
✅ **Streamlit** - Interactive frontend UI  
✅ **OpenAI GPT** - AI-generated lesson content  
✅ **SQLAlchemy** - User authentication & progress tracking  
✅ **Render/Streamlit Cloud** - Deployment-ready  

---  

## 📌 **Key Features**  

### 🎓 **Personalized Learning**  
- Select a **topic** (Python, ML, etc.)  
- Choose a **difficulty level** (Beginner to Advanced)  
- Pick your **learning style** (Theoretical or Practical)  
- **AI-generated lessons** presented in markdown format  

### 🏆 **Gamification & Tracking**  
- **User Authentication**: Register & log in securely  
- **Leaderboard**: Compare scores with other learners  
- **Badges System**: Earn rewards for completing milestones  

### 🔥 **Technical Highlights**  
✅ **FastAPI Backend**: Handles lesson generation & user management  
✅ **Streamlit Frontend**: Provides an intuitive, interactive UI  
✅ **OpenAI Integration**: Uses GPT to generate structured, high-quality lessons  
✅ **Secure Data Management**: Uses `.env` files for API keys & sensitive data  

---  

## 🛠 **Installation & Setup**  

### **Prerequisites**  
📌 Python 3.10+  
📌 OpenAI API Key  

### **Steps to Set Up**  

1️⃣ **Clone the Repository**  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/LearnAgent.git
cd LearnAgent
```  

2️⃣ **Set Up Virtual Environment**  
```bash
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
```  

3️⃣ **Install Dependencies**  
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```  

4️⃣ **Configure Environment Variables**  
Create a `.env` file:  
```bash
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./test.db
```  

5️⃣ **Run the Backend**  
```bash
uvicorn backend.api.main:app --reload
```  

6️⃣ **Run the Frontend**  
```bash
streamlit run frontend/streamlit.py
```  

---  

## 🚀 **Usage Guide**  

📌 **1. Register & Log In** - Secure authentication system  
📌 **2. Generate a Lesson** - Select your preferences & receive AI-generated content  
📌 **3. Track Progress** - View leaderboard & earn badges for achievements  

---  

## 🏗 **Project Structure**  

```
LearnAgent/
├── backend/
│   ├── api/
│   │   └── main.py          # FastAPI backend
│   └── agents/
│       └── agent.py         # AI lesson generation logic
├── frontend/
│   └── streamlit.py         # Streamlit frontend UI
├── .env                     # Environment variables
├── requirements.txt         # Dependencies list
├── README.md                # Project documentation
└── test.db                  # Local SQLite database
```  

---  

## 🌍 **Deployment Guide**  

### **Backend Deployment**  
✅ **Render/Railway/Heroku** - Deploy FastAPI backend  
✅ Ensure environment variables are configured  

### **Frontend Deployment**  
✅ **Streamlit Cloud** - Deploy frontend by connecting GitHub repository  
✅ Add `OPENAI_API_KEY` and backend URL in Streamlit Cloud secrets  

